      "compositionalMoves": [
        "Two-ground page rhythm: --color-ground-warm (#f7f6f5) as default body substrate, --color-ground-alt (#f0efed) for section alternation — never more than these two neutrals plus white.",
        "Hero is always a split left/right composition: copy and interactive widget on the left column, full-bleed photography on the right under a left-edge scrim gradient; never a centered overlay.",
        "One full-bleed editorial moment (ds-feature) allowed per page — the panel floats over the image at bottom-left on desktop; never stack two ds-feature sections.",
        "The 144 emergency affordance lives exclusively in the footer right column, always in --color-emergency (#f43a11), never used decoratively or elsewhere on the page.",
        "Sticky white header carries a dual-bar structure: utility bar (contact / media / language) above a main nav bar (logo + primary-nav + search); no scroll-triggered color change.",
        "Proof or trust metrics appear as a hairline-bordered strip directly below the hero — tabular-num figures in accent-ink, plain-text labels in body weight; one strip per page maximum.",
        "Interactive search floats as a card widget inside the hero column — never a dedicated search page linked from the header."
      ],
